==用法==

<pre>
{{Harvcol | ''作者的姓氏'' | ''出版年'' | ''頁碼'' }}
</pre>

Alternative to using ''Location'', you may also use the following parameters:

p = ''page''
pp = ''pages''

==注意事項== 
* Trivially modified version of Harvard citation; used to display colon for page numbers.
* The first parameter is the author's last name.
* The second parameter is the year of publication.
* The third parameter is the location of the cited material within the reference. This parameter is optional.
* The parameter ''p'' is an optional page parameter (e.g., "<nowiki>{{ Harvcol | Smith | 2006 | p=25 }}</nowiki>" yields: {{Harvcol|Smith|2006|p=25}}.
* The parameter ''pp'' is an optional page range parameter (e.g., "<nowiki>{{Harvcol|Smith|2006 | pp=25-26 }}</nowiki>" yields: {{Harvcol|Smith|2006|pp=25-26}}.
* If ''Ref''=''none'', then no hyperlink is created.

